<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>QR Access</title>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/qrcodejs/qrcode.min.js"></script>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial;
background:linear-gradient(180deg,#3c3f55,#23273c);
color:white;
text-align:center;
}

.header{
margin-top:40px;
font-size:22px;
letter-spacing:1px;
}

.card{
width:85%;
max-width:420px;
margin:30px auto;
background:white;
border-radius:10px;
padding-bottom:20px;
}

.topbar{
background:#e0b34b;
color:white;
padding:12px;
font-size:16px;
border-radius:10px 10px 0 0;
}

.time{
color:#333;
margin-top:10px;
font-size:18px;
}

#qrcode{
margin:15px auto;
width:250px;
}

.refresh{
color:#888;
margin-top:5px;
}

.countdown{
color:#28a745;
font-size:24px;
margin-top:10px;
}

.footer{
width:85%;
margin:30px auto;
color:#f5d9a5;
font-size:15px;
line-height:1.6;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">
V23080280 (NGÔ QUÝ THÌN)
</div>

<div class="card">

<div class="topbar">
将二维码对准扫描器刷码出场
</div>

<div class="time" id="time"></div>

<div id="qrcode"></div>

<div class="refresh" onclick="makeQR()">
刷新二维码
</div>

<div class="countdown" id="countdown">
00:00:00
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
尊敬的员工您好，您已进入企业涉密区域，<br>
出于企业安全考虑，您的手机摄像头将被禁止拍摄，<br>
感谢您的配合。
</div>

<script>

function updateTime(){
let now=new Date()

let y=now.getFullYear()
let m=now.getMonth()+1
let d=now.getDate()

let h=String(now.getHours()).padStart(2,'0')
let mi=String(now.getMinutes()).padStart(2,'0')
let s=String(now.getSeconds()).padStart(2,'0')

document.getElementById("time").innerHTML=
y+"-"+m+"-"+d+" "+h+":"+mi+":"+s
}

setInterval(updateTime,1000)

function makeQR(){

document.getElementById("qrcode").innerHTML=""

let data="ID:V23080280|TIME:"+Date.now()

new QRCode(document.getElementById("qrcode"),{
text:data,
width:250,
height:250,
correctLevel:QRCode.CorrectLevel.H
})

}

makeQR()

setInterval(makeQR,30000)

let seconds=8*3600

function updateCountdown(){

let h=Math.floor(seconds/3600)
let m=Math.floor((seconds%3600)/60)
let s=seconds%60

document.getElementById("countdown").innerHTML=
String(h).padStart(2,'0')+":"+
String(m).padStart(2,'0')+":"+
String(s).padStart(2,'0')

seconds--

}

setInterval(updateCountdown,1000)

</script>

</body>
</html>
